name: Maggie
description: I am a single Mother with a 9 year old SON,he is the best thing that has happened to me in recent times and i am proud to say that. here is my number and this is a way to contact me as i am not a paid member i seek a matured and intelligent man who sees the cup as half full,a man who is ready to love again.I can’t change yesterday and I don’t know about tomorrow but I can celebrate today and that is what I do…t e x t Me..
